i am creating 3 pages using html CSS and Bootstrap 5 
1- Sign Up page : i use first a image logo then connect with google or other paltform like as linkedIn , instagram , facebook etc then i use a form tag for user fill the form , and last a submit btn.
2- Login Page : i use first a image logo then connect with google or other paltform like as linkedIn , instagram , facebook etc then i use a form tag for user fill the form , and last a submit btn.
3- OTP verification Page : i use first a image logo and then i use a star for hide the users ph number from others. And create a form fill tag for input the otp , and last a submit btn.
